@startuml Stock Management - Sequence Diagram (Login & View Stock)
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor User
participant "Vue App" as Vue
participant "Vue Router" as Router
participant "API\n(Express)" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB

User -> Vue : Open app
Vue -> Router : Check route
Router -> Vue : requiresAuth, no token
Vue -> User : Redirect to Login
User -> Vue : Enter username, password
Vue -> API : POST /auth/login\n{ username, password }
API -> DB : Find user, verify password
DB --> API : User document
API --> Vue : 200 OK\n{ token, user }
Vue -> Vue : Store token in localStorage\nRedirect by role
Vue -> API : GET /products\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>
API -> DB : Query products
DB --> API : Products
API --> Vue : 200 OK\n[ products ]
Vue -> User : Display dashboard (stock data)

@enduml
